{"tid":94794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【直擊大麻派對】420HK 壹周刊走去放蛇","createTime":"2017-01-25T13:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T10:44:42.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56c15eac2bba7e71c111d25aee0e9562bd39b281","tid":94794,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:00:02.000Z","msg":"為了爭取大麻合法化，「420」版主Jacky，早前更計劃跟旅行社「金怡假期」合辦一個以大麻為主題的荷蘭旅行團，打正旗號搞迷幻之旅，會否有點過分呢？ <br />\n<br />\nJacky就這樣說：「基於在香港做這事情是不合法，我沒可能拿一棵大麻給你看，甚至乎給你試，我沒可能做這事情，我又想令多些人認識大麻這東西，荷蘭是容許吸食和買賣大麻的，(所以)想帶多些人，認識大麻是什麼。」 <br />\n<br />\nJacky又說，找旅行社合作十分困難，「有一定的困難，因為大部分旅行社，都是一聽到大麻兩個字，就可能已皺眉頭，甚至乎說會覆我，但都是沒有回覆。」但「金怡假期」就強調，他們不是跟Jacky合作，只是Jacky包團，「金怡假期」只是因應客人的需要，替他們訂機票、酒店和當地車輛等。 <br />\n<br />\n其後Jacky和網友公然在聚會上集體「隊草」，未出發先犯法，《壹》仔再向本來跟Jacky合作的「金怡假期」查詢，不願上鏡的負責人魏小姐直認，Jacky已取消包團:「係呀!佢哋已經暫停咗。(咩原因?)我哋唔知道，但係佢哋俾我哋嘅回覆係人數不足。」 <br />\n<br />\n至於會否擔心這種旅行團會鼓吹吸大麻?她說：「其實我哋冇理呢件事，因為呢個只係一個包團，佢只不過同我們講想去咩地方，我哋睇過呢啲地方係安全，合法，亦係公開俾遊客參觀嘅，所以我哋就幫佢哋安排行程，嗰啲地方任何旅客都可以去。」魏小姐強調如他們在行程中吸大麻，旅行社不能干涉亦無需負上責任。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170125/2_472528_0/-%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A%E5%A4%A7%E9%BA%BB%E6%B4%BE%E5%B0%8D-%E5%A0%B1%E5%90%8D%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E5%B0%91-%E5%A4%A7%E9%BA%BB%E6%97%85%E8%A1%8C%E5%9C%98-%E7%88%9B%E5%B0%BE-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170125%2F2_472528_0%2F-%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2593%258A%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%25B0%258D-%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2590%258D%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25B0%2591-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E6%2597%2585%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%259C%2598-%25E7%2588%259B%25E5%25B0%25BE-&d=CplsXHUpDta2qU6L8%2Fp1%2FQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=b4e2c98c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170125%2F2_472528_0%2F-%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2593%258A%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%25B0%258D-%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2590%258D%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25B0%2591-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E6%2597%2585%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%259C%2598-%25E7%2588%259B%25E5%25B0%25BE-&h=c6decc6b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170125/2_472528_0/-%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A%E5%A4%A7%E9%BA%BB%E6%B4%BE%E5%B0%8D-%E5%A0%B1%E5%90%8D%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E5%B0%91-%E5%A4%A7%E9%BA%BB%E6%97%85%E8%A1%8C%E5%9C%98-%E7%88%9B%E5%B0%BE-</a>"},{"pid":"23a8d590658bb74409726d22df6ae259c0cae4fb","tid":94794,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:17:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5226fc482a7d09c8c924761548c23f962195b4c9","tid":94794,"uid":58099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:20:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/66w40uG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F66w40uG.jpg&h=98c8169b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d516f95cd6a90e82c9cce7286bc2c5bef3505e81","tid":94794,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:26:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb948d4ffe94556478942771f34659f322b58b6","tid":94794,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8605e1ea43f473dd8b0a5d25957687202c6c0d8","tid":94794,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37dd8aad1072900fe354ca1efaadf9af9184db6","tid":94794,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:44:42